Class ProtocolBufferMessageBodyProvider

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.dropwizard.jersey.protobuf.ProtocolBufferMessageBodyProvider
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javax.ws.rs.ext.MessageBodyReader<com.google.protobuf.Message>, javax.ws.rs.ext.MessageBodyWriter<com.google.protobuf.Message>

    @Provider
@Consumes("application/x-protobuf")
@Produces({"application/x-protobuf","application/x-protobuf-text-format"})
public class ProtocolBufferMessageBodyProvider
extends java.lang.Object
implements javax.ws.rs.ext.MessageBodyReader<com.google.protobuf.Message>, javax.ws.rs.ext.MessageBodyWriter<com.google.protobuf.Message>
    A Jersey provider which enables using Protocol Buffers to parse request entities into objects and generate response entities from objects.
